<p id="fs-idm243168608">Use this <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://openstaxcollege.org/l/16PhetAtomBld">Build an Atom simulator</a> to build atoms of the first 10 elements, see which isotopes exist, check nuclear stability, and gain experience with isotope symbols.</p>
